#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.load_tensor_descriptor"
msgstr "# triton.language.load_tensor_descriptor"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:4
msgid "简介：该函数用于从张量描述符加载数据块"
msgstr "Introduction: This function is used to load a data block from a tensor descriptor."

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.load_tensor_descriptor(\n"
"    desc: tensor_descriptor_base,\n"
"    offsets: Sequence[constexpr | tensor],\n"
"    _semantic=None\n"
") -> tensor\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specification"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名         | 类型                              | 说明                                                         |\n"
"| ----------- | ------------------------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `desc`      | `tensor_descriptor_base`        | 张量描述符对象，由 `make_tensor_descriptor` 创建，定义了内存布局（形状、步长、块大小等）。 |\n"
"| `offsets`   | `Sequence[constexpr \\| tensor]` | 数据加载的起始偏移量序列，用于指定当前线程块要加载的数据位置                             |\n"
"| `_semantic` | -                               | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                            |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter | Type                             | Description                                                                                |\n"
"|-----------|----------------------------------|--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n"
"| `desc`    | `tensor_descriptor_base`        | Tensor descriptor object, created by `make_tensor_descriptor`, defining the memory layout (shape, stride, block size, etc.). |\n"
"| `offsets` | `Sequence[constexpr \\| tensor]` | Sequence of starting offsets for data loading, used to specify the data position to be loaded by the current thread block. |\n"
"| `_semantic` | -                               | Reserved parameter, currently not supported for external calls.                            |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:14
msgid "返回值：`tensor` - 根据张量描述符内存布局信息，从指定偏移量处加载的数据块"
msgstr "Return value: `tensor` - A data block loaded from the specified offset based on the memory layout information of the tensor descriptor."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:18
msgid "#### 2.2.1 DataType 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.1 DataType Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:20
msgid ""
"|| uint8 | int8 | uint16 | int16 | uint32 | int32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool/int1 |\n"
"|---| ------- | ------ | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----------- |\n"
"|GPU| √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | × |\n"
"|Ascend A2/A3| √ | √ | × | √ | × | √ | × | √ | √ | √ | √ | × |\n"
msgstr ""
"|| uint8 | int8 | uint16 | int16 | uint32 | int32 | uint64 | int64 | fp16 | fp32 | bf16 | bool/int1 |\n"
"|---| ------- | ------ | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | -------- | ------- | ------ | ------ | ------ | ----------- |\n"
"|GPU| √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | √ | × |\n"
"|Ascend A2/A3| √ | √ | × | √ | × | √ | × | √ | √ | √ | √ | × |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:22
msgid "#### 2.2.2 Shape 支持"
msgstr "#### 2.2.2 Shape Support"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:24
msgid ""
"|        | 支持维度范围          |\n"
"| ------ | --------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
"| Ascend | 仅支持 1~5维 tensor |\n"
msgstr ""
"|        | Supported Dimension Range |\n"
"| ------ | ----------------------- |\n"
"| GPU    | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"
"| Ascend | Only supports 1~5D tensor |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:26
msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异，均支持 1 至 5 维张量。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of Shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms, both support 1 to 5 dimensional tensors."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:28
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Limitations"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:30
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:32
msgid "结论：Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint16、uint32、uint64的支持能力（硬件限制）。"
msgstr "Conclusion: Ascend lacks support for uint16, uint32, and uint64 compared to GPU (hardware limitation)."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:34
msgid ""
"| 差异点            | 描述                                                         | 解决途径                                                |\n"
"| ----------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| 绑定使用限制      | `make_tensor_descriptor` / `load_tensor_descriptor` / `store_tensor_descriptor` 需配套使用，不能与 `tl.load()` / `tl.store()` 混用。 | 升级至 Triton 3.4.0 版本同步上游函数（如 `cast`）可解决 |\n"
"| Triton 版本兼容性 | Triton 3.2.0 存在部分函数（如 `cast`）的兼容性问题。建议升级 Triton版本至 3.4.0 来修复绑定限制。 | 升级至 Triton 3.4.0                                     |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Difference | Description | Solution |\n"
"|------------|-------------|----------|\n"
"| Binding usage restriction | `make_tensor_descriptor` / `load_tensor_descriptor` / `store_tensor_descriptor` must be used together and cannot be mixed with `tl.load()` / `tl.store()`. | Upgrading to Triton 3.4.0 to synchronize upstream functions (such as `cast`) can resolve this. |\n"
"| Triton version compatibility | Triton 3.2.0 has compatibility issues with some functions (such as `cast`). It is recommended to upgrade the Triton version to 3.4.0 to fix the binding restriction. | Upgrade to Triton 3.4.0 |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:36
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:38
msgid "`load_tensor_descriptor` 提供两种调用形式："
msgstr "`load_tensor_descriptor` provides two calling forms:"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:40
msgid "* 面向对象方法调用（推荐）"
msgstr "* Object-oriented method invocation (recommended)"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:42
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"value = desc.load(offsets)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:44
msgid "* 函数式接口调用"
msgstr "* Functional interface invocation"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:46
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"value = triton.language.load_tensor_descriptor(desc, offsets)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:48
msgid "以下示例实现了对输入张量 `x` 做就地绝对值计算："
msgstr "The following example implements in-place absolute value computation on the input tensor `x`:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/load_tensor_descriptor.md:50
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def inplace_abs(in_out_ptr, M, N, M_BLOCK: tl.constexpr, N_BLOCK: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    # 创建张量描述符\n"
"    desc = tl.make_tensor_descriptor(\n"
"        in_out_ptr,\n"
"        shape=[M, N],\n"
"        strides=[N, 1],\n"
"        block_shape=[M_BLOCK, N_BLOCK],\n"
"    )\n"
" # 计算当前线程对应的偏移量\n"
"    moffset = tl.program_id(0) * M_BLOCK\n"
"    noffset = tl.program_id(1) * N_BLOCK\n"
" # 加载数据，计算绝对值，存储结果\n"
"    value = desc.load([moffset, noffset])\n"
"    desc.store([moffset, noffset], tl.abs(value))\n"
"## 初始化张量\n"
"M, N = 256, 256\n"
"x = torch.randn(M, N, device=\"npu\")\n"
"## 配置块大小和网格\n"
"M_BLOCK, N_BLOCK = 32, 32\n"
"grid = (M // M_BLOCK, N // N_BLOCK)\n"
"inplace_abs[grid](x, M, N, M_BLOCK, N_BLOCK)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

